name: Degen the Otter
description: From viral sensation to crypto revolution! Degen became internet famous for his heartwarming car videos where he tries to make friends with people at traffic lights. Now he's bringing that same energy to the memecoin space, officially endorsed by the owner! Degen also spreads joy and positivity wherever he goes, just like our community, who build genuine connections. Degen went from millions of views to a ton of holders.
